item.title: SoftLayer_User_Customer_MobileDevice_Type
item.description: SoftLayer_User_Customer_MobileDevice_Type Service Datatype Description Describes a supported class of mobile device. In this the word class is used in the context of classes of consumer electronic devices, the two most prominent examples being mobile phones and tablets. Local createDate Record create date. Type: dateTime description A description of the device Type: string id Indentifier for record. Type: integer
